FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FThe group gathered outside Downing
OL,7,FStreet, where many held placards
OL,8,Fdisplaying photographs of Iran's
OL,9,Fexiled crown prince, Reza Pahlavi,
OL,10,Fbefore marching through Whitehall.
OL,12,FThe demonstration had been organised
OL,13,Fbefore US and Israeli forces carried
OL,14,Fout a series of strikes on Tehran and
OL,15,Fother cities, claiming they were
OL,16,Fconducting a "pre-emptive" action and
OL,17,Fcalling for Iranians to overthrow the
OL,18,Fregime.
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FAt the rally, organisers led call-and-
OL,7,Fresponse chants of: "What do we
OL,8,Fwant?... Regime change"; and: "Who do
OL,9,Fwe want?... Reza Pahlavi".
OL,11,FMany waved an Iranian flag, and
OL,12,Fseveral held signs proclaiming Pahlavi
OL,13,Fto be the rightful leader of the
OL,14,Fcountry, one of which read: "This is
OL,15,Fthe final battle, Pahlavi will return."
OL,17,FIranian national Maryam Mashali, 41,
OL,18,Fsaid she decided to join the protest
OL,19,Ffor her country, its freedom and its
OL,20,Fpeople.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@WO]pD@_OUqD@YO]vD@]OUwD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FMs Mashali escaped Iran and sought
OL,7,Fasylum in Turkey, where she lived for
OL,8,Feight years before coming to the UK,
OL,9,Fwhere she has lived for 10 months.
OL,11,FHer parents, sister and many of her
OL,12,Ffriends still live in Iran and her
OL,13,Fnephew is one of the country's many
OL,14,Fdissidents to have been arrested and
OL,15,Fjailed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,F"My sister's son is in jail. (He has
OL,7,Fspent) three weeks in jail, and I
OL,8,Fdon't have any news of him. We don't
OL,9,Fknow what's happening for him in jail.
OL,10,FI'm sorry to say that we don't even
OL,11,Fknow if he is alive or not," Ms
OL,12,FMashali said.
OL,14,F"It's very hard for us... I really
OL,15,Fworry about them," she said of her
OL,16,Ffamily who remain in Iran.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]vD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FWhen asked how she felt about the
OL,7,Fattacks on Iran that morning, Ms
OL,8,FMashali said: "We are, all of us, very
OL,9,Fhappy. Unfortunately, I am saying
OL,10,Fthis, but we don't have any choice. No
OL,11,Fchoice. We really needed military
OL,12,Fhelp."
OL,14,FShe said she hopes Iran can be made
OL,15,F"better" again so that "the young
OL,16,Fpeople, and all the people in Iran,
OL,17,Fhave the freedom that they deserve".
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@FO]wD@AOUwD@HO]wD@XOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FMs Mashali believes Iran faces many
OL,7,Fdifficulties, and said she feels sure
OL,8,Fthings will change if the regime is
OL,9,Foverthrown.
OL,11,FA Swiss national, who gave his name as
OL,12,FNick, said he had been inspired to
OL,13,Fjoin the protest because "the regime
OL,14,Fis near collapse".
OL,16,FHe said: "I used to work with an
OL,17,FIranian journalist, and working with
OL,18,Fthem and seeing the atrocities this
OL,19,Fregime has created for many years... I
OL,20,Fleft that job ages ago, but the cause
OL,21,Fstill matters to me."
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@QO]xD@JOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,F"This is the time to protest. The
OL,7,Fregime is near collapse... There's a
OL,8,Fchance to take out this government,"
OL,9,Fhe added.
OL,11,FAsked about the US and Israeli
OL,12,Fstrikes, Nick said: "Violence is never
OL,13,Fthe answer, but in (this) case, this
OL,14,Fis the only way to deal with that
OL,15,Fregime ` people collaborating, the
OL,16,Fattacks.
OL,18,F"This is the only language they
OL,19,Funderstand. The time for negotiation
OL,20,Fis over with these people."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]tD@UOUzD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FWhile dozens of demonstrators chanted
OL,7,Fand sang protest songs opposite the
OL,8,Fgates of Downing Street, Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer made a statement to the press
OL,10,Fjust a stone's throw away inside No 10.
OL,12,FSir Keir said British aircraft in the
OL,13,Fregion were "in the sky" as part of
OL,14,F"co-ordinated regional defensive
OL,15,Foperations to protect our people, our
OL,16,Finterests and our allies".
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@XO]vD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
