OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772460675
OL,3,CIran strikes were 'only choice' says
OL,4,CLondon protester whose nephew is jailed
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister joined the German
OL,7,Fand French leaders in calling for Iran
OL,8,Fto "refrain from indiscriminate
OL,9,Fmilitary strikes" and seek a
OL,10,F"negotiated solution".
OL,12,FThe protest, which was peaceful,
OL,13,Flasted around three hours and no
OL,14,Farrests were made.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
